{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1542,"text":"There are 39 million people in the world"},{"time":4386,"text":"who are blind."},{"time":5876,"text":"Eighty percent of them"},{"time":8350,"text":"are living in low-income countries such as Kenya,"},{"time":11169,"text":"and the absolute majority"},{"time":13118,"text":"do not need to be blind."},{"time":14625,"text":"They are blind from diseases"},{"time":16480,"text":"that are either completely curable or preventable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":20256,"text":"Knowing this, with my young family,"},{"time":22768,"text":"we moved to Kenya."},{"time":24162,"text":"We secured equipment,"},{"time":25969,"text":"funds, vehicles, we trained a team,"},{"time":29668,"text":"we set up a hundred clinics throughout"},{"time":31692,"text":"the Great Rift Valley"},{"time":33190,"text":"to try and understand a single question:"},{"time":36651,"text":"why are people going blind,"},{"time":38737,"text":"and what can we do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41656,"text":"The challenges were great."},{"time":44570,"text":"When we got to where we were going,"},{"time":46401,"text":"we set up our high-tech equipment."},{"time":49067,"text":"Power was rarely available."},{"time":51246,"text":"We'd have to run our equipment"},{"time":52099,"text":"from petrol power generators."},{"time":54999,"text":"And then something occurred to me:"},{"time":56946,"text":"There has to be an easier way,"},{"time":59441,"text":"because it's the patients who are the most in need"},{"time":61441,"text":"of access to eye care"},{"time":62999,"text":"who are the least likely to get it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":65340,"text":"More people in Kenya,"},{"time":66446,"text":"and in sub-Saharan Africa,"},{"time":68358,"text":"have access to a mobile phone"},{"time":70149,"text":"than they do clean running water."},{"time":72302,"text":"So we said, could we harness"},{"time":74021,"text":"the power of mobile technology"},{"time":75640,"text":"to deliver eye care in a new way?"},{"time":77791,"text":"And so we developed Peek,"},{"time":79576,"text":"a smartphone [system] that enables"},{"time":82114,"text":"community healthcare workers"},{"time":83626,"text":"and empowers them to deliver eye care everywhere."},{"time":87456,"text":"We set about replacing\ntraditional hospital equipment,"},{"time":90126,"text":"which is bulky, expensive and fragile,"},{"time":92649,"text":"with smartphone apps and hardware"},{"time":94684,"text":"that make it possible to test anyone"},{"time":96821,"text":"in any language and of any age."},{"time":100010,"text":"Here we have a demonstration"},{"time":101814,"text":"of a three-month-old having their vision"},{"time":103537,"text":"accurately tested using an app and an eye tracker."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111650,"text":"We've got many trials going on"},{"time":113393,"text":"in the community and in schools,"},{"time":115593,"text":"and through the lessons that\nwe've learned in the field,"},{"time":117493,"text":"we've realized it's extremely important"},{"time":119196,"text":"to share the data in non-medical jargon"},{"time":122056,"text":"so that people understand"},{"time":123717,"text":"what we're examining and what that means to them."},{"time":126340,"text":"So here, for example,"},{"time":127614,"text":"we use our sight sim application,"},{"time":129470,"text":"once your vision has been measured,"},{"time":131262,"text":"to show carers and teachers"},{"time":133972,"text":"what the visual world is like for that person,"},{"time":136486,"text":"so they can empathize with them and help them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139952,"text":"Once we've discovered somebody has low vision,"},{"time":142340,"text":"the next big challenge is to work out why,"},{"time":144911,"text":"and to be able to do that,"},{"time":146028,"text":"we need to have access to the inside of the eye."},{"time":148529,"text":"Traditionally, this requires expensive equipment"},{"time":151115,"text":"to examine an area called the retina."},{"time":153196,"text":"The retina is the single part of the eye that has"},{"time":156005,"text":"huge amounts of information about the body"},{"time":158101,"text":"and its health."},{"time":159889,"text":"We've developed 3D-printed,"},{"time":161700,"text":"low-cost hardware"},{"time":163141,"text":"that comes in at less than five dollars to produce,"},{"time":165541,"text":"which can then be clipped onto a smartphone"},{"time":168484,"text":"and makes it possible to get views"},{"time":169926,"text":"of the back of the eye"},{"time":171147,"text":"of a very high quality."},{"time":172903,"text":"And the beauty is, anybody can do it."},{"time":176100,"text":"In our trials on over two and half thousand people,"},{"time":178979,"text":"the smartphone with the add-on clip"},{"time":180896,"text":"is comparable to a camera"},{"time":182577,"text":"that is hugely more expensive"},{"time":184472,"text":"and hugely more difficult to transport."}]},{"cues":[{"time":188061,"text":"When we first moved to Kenya,"},{"time":189940,"text":"we went with 150,000 dollars of equipment,"},{"time":192593,"text":"a team of 15 people,"},{"time":195050,"text":"and that was what was\nneeded to deliver health care."},{"time":197942,"text":"Now, all that's needed"},{"time":200307,"text":"is a single person"},{"time":202099,"text":"on a bike with a smartphone."},{"time":205495,"text":"And it costs just 500 dollars."},{"time":209349,"text":"The issue of power supply"},{"time":211219,"text":"is overcome by harnessing the power of solar."},{"time":213780,"text":"Our healthcare workers travel"},{"time":214920,"text":"with a solar-powered rucksack"},{"time":216465,"text":"which keeps the phone charged and backed up."},{"time":218926,"text":"Now we go to the patient"},{"time":221196,"text":"rather than waiting for the patient never to come."},{"time":223907,"text":"We go to them in their homes"},{"time":225640,"text":"and we give them the most comprehensive,"},{"time":227437,"text":"high-tech, accurate examination,"},{"time":229377,"text":"which can be delivered by\nanyone with minimal training."},{"time":233481,"text":"We can link global experts"},{"time":236318,"text":"with people in the most rural,"},{"time":238060,"text":"difficult-to-reach places"},{"time":239250,"text":"that are beyond the end of the road,"},{"time":240839,"text":"effectively putting those experts in their homes,"},{"time":243353,"text":"allowing us to make diagnoses"},{"time":245331,"text":"and make plans for treatment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248399,"text":"Project managers, hospital directors,"},{"time":251126,"text":"are able to search on our interface"},{"time":253045,"text":"by any parameter they may be interested in."},{"time":255047,"text":"Here in Nakuru, where I've been living,"},{"time":257070,"text":"we can search for people"},{"time":258406,"text":"by whatever condition."},{"time":259850,"text":"Here are people who are blind"},{"time":261122,"text":"from a curable condition cataract."},{"time":263652,"text":"Each red pin depicts somebody"},{"time":265681,"text":"who is blind from a disease that is curable"},{"time":268338,"text":"and treatable, and they're locatable."},{"time":270584,"text":"We can use bulk text messaging services"},{"time":272468,"text":"to explain that we're coming to arrange a treatment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":275622,"text":"What's more, we've learned that this is something"},{"time":278237,"text":"that we haven't built just for the community"},{"time":280275,"text":"but with the community."},{"time":281860,"text":"Those blue pins that drop represent"},{"time":284112,"text":"elders, or local leaders,"},{"time":286213,"text":"that are connected to those people"},{"time":287452,"text":"who can ensure that we can find them"},{"time":288785,"text":"and arrange treatment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290886,"text":"So for patients like Mama Wangari,"},{"time":293888,"text":"who have been blind for over 10 years"},{"time":295484,"text":"and never seen her grandchildren,"},{"time":297113,"text":"for less than 40 dollars, we can restore her eyesight."},{"time":300931,"text":"This is something that has to happen."},{"time":306209,"text":"It's only in statistics"},{"time":307840,"text":"that people go blind by the millions."},{"time":310563,"text":"The reality is everyone goes blind on their own."},{"time":314431,"text":"But now, they might just be"},{"time":316408,"text":"a text message away from help."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318547,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":325295,"text":"And now because live demos are always a bad idea,"},{"time":327426,"text":"we're going to try a live demo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":329224,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":330480,"text":"So here we have the Peek Vision app."},{"time":340142,"text":"Okay, and what we're looking at here,"},{"time":342786,"text":"this is Sam's optic nerve,"},{"time":344281,"text":"which is a direct extension of her brain,"},{"time":346680,"text":"so I'm actually looking at her brain as we look there."},{"time":349289,"text":"We can see all parts of the retina."},{"time":352820,"text":"It makes it possible to pick up diseases"},{"time":355350,"text":"of the eye and of the body"},{"time":357517,"text":"that would not be possible without access to the eye,"},{"time":360046,"text":"and that clip-on device can be manufactured"},{"time":361981,"text":"for just a few dollars,"},{"time":363531,"text":"and people can be cured of blindness,"},{"time":365162,"text":"and I think it says a lot about us as a human race"},{"time":368385,"text":"if we've developed cures and we don't deliver them."},{"time":370910,"text":"But now we can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":372108,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374324,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}